{
  "texts": [
    "With changes in work shifts and occurrence of unanticipated work-related duties, it may not be feasible to expect 85% of LEOs to attend 6 or more sessions.",
    "Alternative formats for the course may thus be worth exploring, such as an immersion-based delivery of MBRT with the same overall intervention time delivered over 2 days followed by remotely-delivered brief \"booster\" sessions.",
    "Preliminary data suggests this model is feasible and results in similar outcomes as an 8-week model [128].",
    "At the 6-month follow-up, retention (83.6%) exceeded our benchmark (≤ 20% attrition).",
    "Attrition rates in previous mindfulness training trials with LEOs have been variable, ranging from 7% attrition at 5-month follow up [74] to up to 41% at the end of the 8-week intervention [78]."
  ]
}